main.bio: I have over 2 years of experience as a software engineer. While I'm a proficient Full Stack Developer, my expertise is building scalable backend API services and enterprise websites as well. I love building things. While hard engineering problems are often intrinsically fun to tackle, I'm most attracted to solve real customer problems with a business justification. I’ve mostly worked professionally with JavaScript, TypeScript and Python but also a little bit with PHP and Java.
